titleStmt.title: By the Kings Maiesties commissioners for granting court leets

notesStmt.note: Announcing where qualified persons may apply for new or renewed warrants to hold such courts.

"The Commissioners for this grant. [brace] Sir Francis Bacon ...(name has been crossed off by pen); Sir Henry Yeluerton, Knight; Sir Edward Moseley, Knight; Sir Robert Beuill, Knight; Edward Woodward, Esquire; Roger Wood, Gentleman."
Reproduction of original in: Society of Antiquaries.
